$ Perl module HTML::Entities

`HTML::Entities` takes a string and *encodes* it to use → development/web/HTML/entities[HTML entities], or takes a (HTML-)text (with HTML entities) and *decodes* it into a »normal« string.

gh|PerlModules|/HTML/Entities/script.pl||

→ development/languages/Perl/modules/index[Perl modules].

sa:
  → development/languages/Perl/modules/HTML/Escape
